name: Impregnation Hentai 2.5 + Alpha and Beta models
description:
Impregnation Hentai 2.5

if you wanna enter my small discord server to discuss about my LoRA's: https://discord.gg/jqmqnkdNBZ

Alpha is a model that has 2x the dataset in size than 2.5, outperforms 2.5 when very accurate tags are entered, but fails miserable to produce content at very few prompts.
Beta is a model has a performance between 2.5 and Alpha, has the same dataset as Alpha but with fewer epochs. Please give me feedback so I can update this model page is Alpha or Beta is better so it can be titled 3.0, but for now, 2.5, seems stable both for few prompt gens and very intricate prompt gens.

Recommandations:

Interrogate a picture you generated that you like with the LoRA on with deepdanbooru and paste it back in text to image and you will get decent results.

Recommended use of tags such as: fertilization, sperm cell, ovum, sperm meets egg

If you would like to buy me a small coffee to keep me up at night, it will be much appreciated!! https://ko-fi.com/grendar
